#---
# purpose: "source-order item macro returns compiler-shaped quoted function source"
# paths: [fz2-run, fz2-interp, fz2-build]
# kind: run
#---
#
# # item_macro_source
#
# Defines an item macro that returns a quoted function definition as
# compiler-shaped AST. Source production expands the item macro, applies the
# returned compiler fragment, and later code calls the generated function.
defmacro make_answer() do
  {:fn, %{}, [{:answer, %{}, []}, [{:do, 42}]]}
end

make_answer()

fn main(), do: dbg(answer())
